          "_name": "article12",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article12\" group=\"Article\">    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4 mt-0\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\"><b>Disclaimer&nbsp;</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">The storytelling magic of photos\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>Effective Date: June 2025\n<br>Website: https://jobfinds4u.co.za\n</b><br><b><br>This Disclaimer governs your use of our website and the services, tools, and resources provided on or through the Site. By accessing or using JobFinds4U, you accept and agree to the terms of this Disclaimer in full. If you disagree with any part of this Disclaimer, please do not use the website.\n</b><br>\n<b><br>1. General Information\n</b><br>All content on this website is provided for informational and educational purposes only. While we strive to keep information accurate and up to date, JobFinds4U makes no guarantees regarding the accuracy, reliability, or completeness of any content. You use the information at your own risk.\n<br>\n<br>We reserve the right to make changes to the site, including removing, modifying, or updating content, services, or policies without prior notice.\n<br>\n<b><br>2. No Employment Guarantee\n</b><br>JobFinds4U does not offer employment or guarantee job placement. We are a job listing and career resource platform that aggregates job opportunities, tools, and advice to assist job seekers. However, we are not involved in the hiring process and do not influence or control the decisions made by third-party employers.\n<br>\n<br>While we aim to present legitimate job opportunities, we cannot verify every listing. It is the responsibility of each user to verify the legitimacy of any employer, job post, or recruiter before applying, interviewing, or sharing personal information.\n<br>\n<br>We strongly encourage users to be cautious of potential scams, phishing attempts, or fraudulent offers.\n<br>\n<br><b>3. No Legal, Financial, or Career Advice\n</b><br>The information shared on JobFinds4U — including blog posts, guides, and digital products — does not constitute professional advice of any kind. This includes but is not limited to:\n<br>\n<br>• Legal advice\n<br>• Financial or tax advice\n<br>• Employment contract review\n<br>• Mental health or counseling services\n<br>\n<br>If you need professional advice, you should seek a licensed or qualified expert in your respective field.\n<br>\n<br><b>4. Third-Party Content &amp; External Links\n</b><br>Our website may include links to third-party websites, services, or tools. These external links are provided for your convenience and do not signify endorsement. JobFinds4U is not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party websites or services.\n<br>\n<br>We make no representations or warranties about the content, functionality, or accuracy of third-party websites and will not be liable for any damages or losses arising from your use of them.\n<br>\n<br><b>5. Affiliate Disclaimer\n</b><br>From time to time, JobFinds4U may participate in affiliate marketing programs. This means we may earn a small commission if you click a link on our site and make a purchase through a third-party website. These commissions help support the maintenance and growth of our platform.\n<br>\n<br>We only promote products and services we believe are helpful or relevant to our audience. However, any financial decisions made using affiliate resources should be done at your own discretion and with full understanding of the risks involved.\n<br>\n<br><b>6. No Warranties\n</b><br>JobFinds4U is provided on an “as-is” and “as-available” basis. To the fullest extent permitted by law, we disclaim all warranties, express or implied, including but not limited to:\n<br>\n<br>• Merchantability\n<br>• Fitness for a particular purpose\n<br>• Non-infringement\n<br>• Accuracy and completeness of information\n<br>• Site availability or error-free operation\n<br>• We do not warrant that the website or any of its content will be:\n<br>• Always available or uninterrupted\n<br>• Free of viruses, malware, or other harmful components\n<br>• Accurate, complete, or suitable for your personal or professional needs\n<br>\n<br><b>7. Limitation of Liability\n</b><br>To the maximum extent permitted by law, JobFinds4U and its founders, contributors, or affiliates shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or special damages arising out of or in connection with your use of the Site.\n<br>\n<br>This includes, without limitation, damages for:\n<br>\n<br>• Loss of job opportunity or income\n<br>• Personal or professional setbacks\n<br>• Breach of data privacy caused by third-party links\n<br>• Site downtime or technical issues\n<br>\n<br><b>8. User Responsibility\n</b><br>By using JobFinds4U, you agree that:\n<br>\n<br>• You are solely responsible for any decisions made based on content from this Site.\n<br>• You will not hold JobFinds4U liable for any outcomes resulting from advice, tools, or third-party interactions.\n<br>• You will comply with all applicable laws in relation to job applications, employment, and digital conduct.\n<br>\n<br><b>9. All articles published on this website are original content written by the owner of JobFinds. The information is based on personal knowledge, professional experience, and research.\n</b><br>While we aim to keep the content accurate and up-to-date, it is intended for informational purposes only and should not be considered legal or professional advice.\n<br>\n<br><b>10.Image Source Notice:\n</b><br>All images used on this website are either owned by JobFinds or sourced from Pixabay.com under the Pixabay License. These images are free for commercial use and do not require attribution. However, we acknowledge and appreciate the artists and contributors on Pixabay for making their work available to the public.\n<br>\n<br><b>11. Updates to This Disclaimer\n</b><br>We reserve the right to update or revise this Disclaimer at any time. All changes will be reflected with a new “Last Updated” date at the top of the page. Continued use of the website after changes are posted constitutes your acceptance of the updated Disclaimer.\n<br>\n<br>Thank you for using <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">JobFinds.</a> We wish you success in your job search!</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
