          "_name": "article12",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article12\" group=\"Article\">    \n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4 mt-0\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\"><b>Terms &amp; Conditions</b></h3>\n                <h4 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">The storytelling magic of photos\n                </h4>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>Last updated: June 1, 2025\n</b><br>\n<br><b>Welcome to JobFinds! These Terms and Conditions (\"Terms\") govern your use of our website located at https://jobfinds4u.co.za (\"Site\") and the services we provide (collectively, \"Services\"). By accessing or using JobFinds, you agree to comply with and be bound by these Terms. If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use our Services.\n</b><br>\n<b><br>1. Acceptance of Terms\n</b><br>By using JobFinds, you confirm that you are at least 18 years old or accessing the Services under parental or guardian supervision. You agree to abide by all applicable laws and regulations when using the Site and Services.\n<br>\n<br><b>2. Description of Services\n</b><br>JobFinds provides job listings, career resources, articles, and digital products designed to help job seekers find employment and assist employers in recruiting candidates. We also offer advertising and promotional services related to jobs.\n<br>\n<br><b>3. User Accounts\n</b><br>Some features may require creating a user account.<br>You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information during registration.<br>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials.<br>You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.\n<br>\n<br><b>4. User Conduct\n</b><br>When using JobFinds, you agree that you will not:\n<br>\n<br><b>JobFinds\n</b><br>• Violate any laws or regulations.\n<br>• Post false, misleading, or fraudulent information.\n<br>• Use automated scripts or bots to scrape or harvest data.\n<br>• Upload or distribute viruses, malware, or harmful content.\n<br>• Harass, abuse, or harm other users.\n<br>• Use the Site for any unlawful or unauthorized purpose.\n<br>\n<br><b>5. Job Listings and Content\n</b><br>JobFinds aggregates and displays job listings submitted by third-party employers or sourced from external partners.\n<br>\n<br>• We do not guarantee the accuracy, legality, or completeness of any job postings.\n<br>• Users should perform due diligence before applying to or accepting any job.\n<br>• JobFinds is not an employer and does not directly offer employment.\n<br>• Content published on the Site, including articles, blogs, and resources, is for informational purposes only and does not constitute professional advice.\n<br>\n<br><b>6. Intellectual Property\n</b><br>All content on JobFinds, including text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of JobFinds or its licensors and is protected by copyright and other intellectual property laws.<br>You may not copy, reproduce, distribute, modify, or create derivative works without our explicit permission.<br>Users retain ownership of content they submit but grant JobFinds a non-exclusive license to display and use it in connection with the Services.\n<br>\n<br><b>7. Third-Party Links and Services\n</b><br>JobFinds may contain links to external websites or services not operated or controlled by us.<br>We do not endorse or assume responsibility for third-party content, privacy policies, or practices.<br>Your interactions with third parties are at your own risk.\n<br>\n<br><b>8. Privacy\n</b><br>Your use of JobFinds is also governed by our Privacy Policy, which explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. Please review it carefully.\n<br>\n<br><b>9. Disclaimers and Limitation of Liability\n</b><br>JobFinds provides the Site and Services \"as is\" and makes no warranties or representations regarding accuracy, reliability, or availability.<br>We do not guarantee job placement, earnings, or results from using our Services.<br>To the fullest extent permitted by law, JobFinds and its affiliates are not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of your use of the Site or Services.<br>We are not responsible for any damages or losses caused by your reliance on job postings or third-party content.\n<br>\n<br><b>10. Indemnification\n</b><br>You agree to indemnify and hold harmless JobFinds, its owners, employees, and partners from any claims, damages, losses, liabilities, and expenses arising from your violation of these Terms or your misuse of the Site.\n<br>\n<br><b>11. Termination\n</b><br>We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to JobFinds at any time, without notice, for conduct that violates these Terms or is harmful to other users or the Site.\n<br>\n<br><b>12. Changes to Terms\n</b><br>JobFinds may update these Terms from time to time. When changes occur, we will post the updated Terms here with a new effective date. Your continued use of the Site after changes means you accept the revised Terms.\n<br>\n<br><b>13. Governing Law and Jurisdiction\n</b><br>These Terms are governed by the laws of South Africa. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of JobFinds will be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts located in South Africa.\n<br>\n<br><b>14. Contact Us\n</b><br>If you have questions or concerns about these Terms, please contact us at:\n<br>\n<br>Email: jobfinds4u@gmail.com\n<br>Address: Centurion, Gauteng, South Africa\n<br>\n<br>Thank you for using <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">JobFinds</a>. We wish you success in your job search!&nbsp;<br></p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
