          "_name": "features013",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features13 start\" group=\"Features\" mbr-class=\"{ 'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n      <header>Size</header>\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n      <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n      <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n      <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"cardsWidth\">\n        <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n        <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n        <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n        <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n        <option value=\"2\" selected>6</option>\n      </select>\n      <header>Show/Hide</header>\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\" checked>\n      <header>Cards</header>\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"autoSize\" title=\"Auto Size\">\n      <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageHeight\" title=\"Height\" min=\"1\" max=\"5\" step=\"1\" value=\"2\" condition=\"autoSize && !(showButtons==false && showCardSubtitle==false && showCardTitle==false && showText==false)\">\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Spacing\" name=\"spacing\" checked>\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardTitle\" title=\"Title\" checked>\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showCardSubtitle\" title=\"Subtitle\">\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showText\" title=\"Text\">\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\">\n      <header>Background</header>\n      <fieldset type=\"background\" parallax name=\"bg\" required>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n      </fieldset>\n      <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#edefeb\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n      <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.6\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type == 'image'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\"></div>\n<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n  <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n      <div class=\"mbr-section-head mb-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n        <h4 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>The Best Companies to Work for in South Africa in 2026</b></h4>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">If you're considering embarking on a career journey in South Africa, you're in for an exciting adventure. The country is home to a vibrant job market brimming with opportunities, featuring companies that not only excel in their respective fields but also place a strong emphasis on employee well-being, personal growth, and innovative practices. Whether you’re a veteran in your profession or just stepping onto the career ladder, discovering which organizations foster the most enriching work environments can be key to shaping your future.\n<div>\n</div><div>In this in-depth guide, we'll explore the top companies to work for in South Africa in 2026, illuminating the unique qualities that distinguish them from the rest. We’ll uncover how these companies cultivate exceptional work cultures and what drives their commitment to their employees, all while providing you with valuable insights on how to seize opportunities with these industry leaders. Get ready to discover your next potential workplace!\n</div><div><br></div><br><div>Why These Companies Stand Out\n</div><div>Before we dive headfirst into the complex specifics, it’s essential to first recognize the essential traits that propel these companies to the pinnacle of employment prestige. Grasping these core attributes will shed light on what distinguishes them in the fiercely competitive arena of the job market.</div></h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"row mbr-section-content\">\n    <div class=\"item features-image col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n      <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"item-img\">\n          <a href=\"https://jobs.vodafone.com/careers?start=0&pid=563018694903087&sort_by=timestamp\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/download-255x148.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title data-slide-to=\"0\" data-bs-slide-to=\"0\"></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item-content align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n          <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n            <b>Vodacom</b></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, adipiscing elit.\n          </h6>\n          <p class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n            20 may, 20 min\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"item features-image col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n      <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"item-img\">\n          <a href=\"https://careers.ey.com/ey\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/download201-270x148.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\"></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item-content align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n          <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Ernst &amp; Young (EY)</b></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, adipiscing elit.\n          </h6>\n          <p class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n            20 may, 20 min\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"item features-image col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n      <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"item-img\">\n          <a href=\"https://careers.theheinekencompany.com/SouthAfrica/search/?createNewAlert=false&q=&locationsearch=\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/heinekenbvg-green.svg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\"></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item-content align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n          <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Heineken Beverages</b></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, adipiscing elit.\n          </h6>\n          <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n            20 may, 20 min\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"item features-image col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n      <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"item-img\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.sasol.com/careers/experienced-hires\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/sasol-new-logo-229x86.png\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title data-slide-to=\"3\" data-bs-slide-to=\"3\"></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item-content align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n          <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n            <b>Sasol</b></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, adipiscing elit.\n          </h6>\n          <p class=\"item-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n            20 may, 20 min\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"item features-image col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n      <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"item-img\">\n          <a href=\"https://ehle.fa.em2.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX_1/jobs\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mtn-logo.svg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title data-slide-to=\"4\" data-bs-slide-to=\"4\"></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item-content align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n          <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\">\n            <b>MTN Group&nbsp;</b></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, adipiscing elit.\n          </h6>\n          <p class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n            20 may, 20 min\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"item features-image col-6 col-md-4 col-lg-{{cardsWidth}}\">\n      <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n        <div class=\"item-img\">\n          <a href=\"https://www.standardbank.com/sbg/standard-bank-group/careers/apply/jobs/view-all-jobs\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/download-162x148.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" title data-slide-to=\"5\" data-bs-slide-to=\"5\"></a>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item-content align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle || showCardSubtitle || showText || showButtons\">\n          <h5 class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardTitle\"><b>Standard Bank Group</b></h5>\n          <h6 class=\"item-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-subtitle, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showCardSubtitle\">\n            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, adipiscing elit.\n          </h6>\n          <p class=\"item-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showText\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" data-app-selector=\".item-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n            20 may, 20 min\n          </p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer mt-2\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Start Now</a>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v5ztuxHfv7",
          "_anchor": "features013-2v",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
