          "_name": "news06",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"news06\" group=\"News\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <header>Image</header>\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Height\" name=\"imageHeight\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Main Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Main Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Price\" name=\"showPrice\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n    <header>Color</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"rowColor\" value=\"#1f6463\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mbr-section-maintitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-maintitle\"><b>Business and Side Hustle Hub</b></h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4 mbr-section-mainsubtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-mainsubtitle\">Welcome to the Business &amp; Side Hustle Hub, your go-to space for turning ideas into income. Whether you’re exploring freelancing, online businesses, or creative side hustles, we share guides, workshops, and success stories to help you build financial freedom step by step.</h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center item features-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 \">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n              <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"../_images/hightlights/6.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg col-md-12\">\n              <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Top 10 Side Hustles in South Africa</b></h5>\n                <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                  July 12-13, 2025\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                  Groceries are more expensive than ever, fuel prices keep rising, and electricity bills seem to double overnight. For many South Africans, even with a full-time job, salaries just aren’t stretching far enough to cover daily expenses. Sound familiar? You’re not alone — millions of South Africans are turning to side hustles to close the gap. From tutoring and delivery services to selling products online, side hustles have become more than just a trend — they’re a survival tool. The best part? With just a phone, an internet connection, and a little creativity, you can start your own side hustle today and build financial breathing room for yourself and your family.\n                </p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-white\" href=\"page8.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Read More</a></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center item features-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n              <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-883x589.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg col-md-12\">\n              <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>How to Start a Small Business with Under R1,000</b></h5>\n                <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                  March 15, 2025\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                  Think starting a business needs big money? Not true. In this guide, we share 10 low-cost business ideas you can launch with under R1,000 — from food and beauty services to digital hustles and reselling. Each idea comes with startup tips, costs, and earning potential so you can turn a small investment into a steady income stream in 2025.\n                </p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-white\" href=\"page9.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Read More</a></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div><div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center item features-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n              <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1-1920x1280.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"2\" data-bs-slide-to=\"3\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg col-md-12\">\n              <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Beginner’s Guide to Dropshipping &amp; E-commerce in South Africa</b></h5>\n                <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                  March 15, 2025\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                  Want to launch an online store but don’t have money for stock? Dropshipping lets you sell without holding inventory. This guide covers how to choose products, find suppliers, set up your store, and market it effectively in 2025 — everything you need to start your e-commerce journey in South Africa.\n                </p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-white\" href=\"page10.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Read More&nbsp;</a></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div><div class=\"row justify-content-center align-items-center item features-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n              <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1920x1218.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"3\" data-bs-slide-to=\"4\">\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg col-md-12\">\n              <div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Beginner’s Guide to Freelancing</b></h5>\n                <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showPrice\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                  March 15, 2025\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">\n                  Want to work for yourself and attract international clients? This beginner’s guide explains how to start freelancing, find your first client, and grow into a R10K+/month career in South Africa.\n                </p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-lg btn-white\" href=\"page11.html\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\" target=\"_blank\">Read More&nbsp;</a></div>\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v5K3sDiAkd",
          "_anchor": "news06-30",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
