          "_name": "header16",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"header16\" group=\"Headers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\" condition=\"showImage\">\n\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Menu Items\" name=\"menuItems\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#260a30\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n  <div class=\"text-center\" mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"image-wrap\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-2-1695x1130.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 content-head\">\n        <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mt-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Why Signing Employment Contracts During Mercury Retrograde Might Be a Bad Idea</b></h1>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Astrology-based—use at your own discretion\n<br>\n<br>Did you know that Mercury Retrograde, an astrological phenomenon, can affect communication, technology, and even business transactions? Although some may consider it mere superstition, many believe that it can impact important aspects of life. For instance, it is commonly advised to exercise caution when signing crucial documents such as employment contracts, lease agreements, and business deals during Mercury retrograde periods. It is better to be safe than sorry, so be mindful of this astrological event and take the necessary precautions to protect yourself and your business.<br><br><br>What is Mercury Retrograde?\n<br>\n<br>Mercury retrograde usually happens 3 times a year, lasting approximately 3 weeks every time. During this period, astrologers caution that the influence of Mercury can lead to misunderstandings, delays, regret, and communication errors. This phenomenon is said to affect not only verbal and written communication but also technological devices and travel plans. You don’t have to believe in astrology, remember, there is free will, and it affects everyone differently. I have experienced making huge decisions during this time, which included starting a new business that failed months later, moving to a new apartment that I was not happy about, buying a sound bar that broke, and, oh yes, signing that contract!!! And guess what I wasn't happy in that role at all and resigned a few months later.\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>The Impact on Employment Contracts:\n<br>\n<br>An employment contract is a crucial commitment for both employers and employees. It lays out the expectations of employment, such as job duties, pay, perks, and other relevant information. During the Mercury retrograde period, there is a higher likelihood of miscommunication and misunderstandings. As a result, it may not be the best time to enter into such agreements..\n<br>\n<br>Reasons to Avoid Signing Employment Contracts During Mercury Retrograde:\n<br>\n<br>Misunderstandings – Mercury retrograde is often associated with confusion and misinterpretation. This could lead to ambiguities in the contract language or miscommunication regarding terms and conditions, potentially causing issues down the line.\n<br><br>\n<br>Delays and Revisions – Contracts signed during Mercury retrograde may be subject to delays and revisions. What seemed clear and straightforward at the time of signing could later require extensive modifications or renegotiations due to overlooked details or unforeseen complications. This can result in frustration, wasted time, and extra expenses.\n<br>\n<br>Unforeseen Changes – Mercury retrograde is notorious for bringing unexpected changes and disruptions. Signing an employment contract during this time could increase the likelihood of unforeseen circumstances arising that impact the terms of employment or the stability of the company.\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>Technology Glitches – In today’s digital age, many employment contracts are signed electronically. Mercury's retrograde influence on technology may heighten the risk of glitches or errors in the electronic signing process, potentially leading to incomplete or invalid contracts.\n<br>\n<br>Long-Term Implications – Employment contracts often have long-term implications for both parties involved. Making such a significant commitment during a period of cosmic unrest may not bode well for the future stability and success of the employment relationship.\n<br>\n<br>Regrettable Decisions: Retrograde periods are notorious for clouding judgment and fostering a sense of impulsivity. What may seem like a good idea during Mercury retrograde could later be regretted once clarity is restored. Avoid making hasty decisions, especially those with long-term consequences, and take the time to carefully evaluate all options before committing to any contract.\n<br>\n<br>Financial Losses: Mercury retrograde can bring about unexpected financial setbacks and losses. Signing a contract during this period may expose you to risks that you hadn’t anticipated, such as hidden fees, unfavourable terms, or unforeseen circumstances that impact your financial stability. Proceeding with caution during the Mercury retrograde can help mitigate these risks and protect your financial interests.\n<br>\n<br>\n<b><br>Mercury Retrograde Dates for 2026:\n</b><br>\n<br><b>For those who are cautious about astrological influences, here are the Mercury retrograde dates for the year 2026:\n</b><br>\n<br>• February 26-March 20, 2026\n<br>• June 29-July 23, 2026\n<br>• October 24-November 13, 2026\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>Just wanted to give you a friendly heads-up that there's something you should be aware of. It's going to be preceded by a pre-shadow phase that'll start two weeks before the actual Mercury Retrograde, followed by a post-shadow phase that'll bring the same energy. So, just be careful during these times and stay on your toes to avoid any surprises. With a bit of caution and care, we can together make sure that everything goes smoothly and we have a fantastic period!\n<br>\n<br>Make the most of this period with these exciting activities!\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>Reflect and review: Use this time to reflect on past decisions, experiences, and relationships. It's an excellent opportunity to review your goals and plans.\n<br>\n<br>Re-evaluate: Reassess your priorities and make adjustments if necessary. Mercury retrograde can highlight areas of your life that need attention or re-evaluation.\n<br>\n<br>Communicate with care: Be mindful of your communication during this time, as misunderstandings and miscommunications may be more prevalent. Please make sure to be clear and concise in your communication.\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>Complete unfinished tasks: Mercury retrograde is a good time to tie up loose ends and finish projects that you've been putting off.\n<br>\n<br>Back up data: Given the potential for technological glitches during Mercury retrograde, it's a good idea to back up important data and files to avoid any potential loss.\n<br>\n<br>Practice patience: Be prepared for delays and setbacks, whether in travel, work, or personal matters. In the current situation, it's crucial to cultivate patience and adaptability.\n<br>\n<br>Focus on introspection: Spend time in introspection and self-reflection. Consider journaling, meditation, or other mindfulness practices to connect with your inner self.\n<br>\n<br>Reconnect with old friends: Mercury retrograde can bring opportunities to reconnect with people from your past. Reach out to old friends or acquaintances and catch up with them, not past lovers, please!\n<br>\n<br>Prepare for the future: Use this time to plan and prepare for the future, but avoid taking definitive action until Mercury retrograde has ended.\n<br><br>\n<br>Sometimes, it does happen that you need to sign that contract or venture into that new opportunity during mercury retrograde. That’s also okay because there is nothing else you can do about it.\n<br>\n<br>While opinions about Mercury retrogrades may differ, many individuals and businesses exercise caution during these periods. This is especially true when it comes to signing essential documents such as employment contracts. Whether you believe in astrology or not, it's advisable to be mindful of potential communication challenges and disruptions during Mercury retrogrades. This could save you from future headaches and uncertainties in your professional endeavors. As always, it's crucial to carefully weigh the risks and benefits before making significant decisions, especially during astrologically turbulent times.\n<br>\n<br>Other Article: <a href=\"page5.html\" class=\"text-danger\" target=\"_blank\"><b>How to Land a Job in South Africa in 30 Days or Less</b></a><br></p>\n        <div class=\"row-links mt-4\" mbr-if=\"menuItems > 0\">\n          <ul class=\"header-menu\" mbr-list mbr-list-grow=\"menuItems\">\n            <li mbr-text class=\"header-menu-item mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" data-app-selector=\"header-menu-item\">\n              <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-secondary\">Shop</a>\n            </li>\n            \n            \n            \n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v5Kmofnt87",
