          "_name": "timeline02",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"timeline02\" group=\"News\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"7\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" value=\"8\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Event\" name=\"showTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Navigating Success: A Guide for New Employees in the Workplace</b></h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image active\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"></p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>The New Job</b></h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>The New Job</b><br>Venturing into a new job opportunity can stir up a whirlwind of emotions, from the exhilaration of embarking on a fresh journey to the apprehension of navigating uncharted waters. As a freshly appointed team member, you're treading into unfamiliar territory with a keen desire to leave a positive mark and thrive in your new role. While the initial phase may appear daunting, embracing the appropriate mindset and approaches can lay the groundwork for triumph and create a lasting impact within your new professional sphere.\n<br>\n<br><b>Embrace a Learning Mindset\n</b><br>Approach your new role with humility and a genuine eagerness to learn. Recognize that you may not have all the answers right away, and that's perfectly acceptable. Adopt a proactive attitude by asking questions, seeking input, and gathering as much information as possible about your role, the company's culture, and operational procedures. A mindset focused on continuous learning will not only accelerate your advancement but also demonstrate your commitment to both personal and professional growth. Always remember that asking questions, especially when you are unsure about a task, is crucial for avoiding mistakes and enhancing your performance.&nbsp;<br></p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-2-1920x1280.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          2010\n        </p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"></h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>Build Relationships\n</b><br>Establishing meaningful and positive relationships with your colleagues, managers, and key stakeholders is one of the most effective ways to integrate into a new workplace. Start by personally introducing yourself to each individual and engaging in genuine conversations to form authentic connections. Showing a sincere interest in your coworkers fosters a sense of belonging and teamwork within the professional environment. Additionally, nurturing these relationships can open doors to collaboration, guidance, and career development opportunities.\n<br>\n<b><br>Seek Clarity and Feedback\n</b><br>It's essential to have open and detailed discussions with your manager to fully understand your role, responsibilities, and performance objectives. Schedule regular meetings to track your progress, address any potential challenges, and receive valuable feedback. It's also beneficial to seek input from your peers, as their perspectives can guide you in improving your skills. Establishing a strong professional relationship with your manager will lay the groundwork for effective communication and support.\n<br>\n<br><b>Continuously Learn and Grow\n</b><br>Make a commitment to lifelong learning and professional development. Seek out opportunities to improve your skills through training programs, workshops, certifications, and staying updated on industry trends and best practices. Investing in your education not only enhances your capabilities but also establishes you as a valuable asset to your organization. By continuously developing your skill set, you ensure that you remain relevant and contribute effectively to your team's success.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1139x759.webp\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
