          "_name": "timeline02",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"timeline02\" group=\"News\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\" checked>\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" value=\"8\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Event\" name=\"showTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n          <b>Timeline</b>\n        </h3>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.</h5>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image active\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          2018\n        </p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n          <b>Award-winning photographer</b>\n        </h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>Demonstrate Initiative and Accountability\n</b><br>Display a strong sense of ownership and proactivity in your role by taking the lead on new projects and presenting creative and original ideas that surpass basic expectations. Actively seek out opportunities to make meaningful contributions to your team's accomplishments and hold yourself accountable for the outcomes of your decisions. Ensure prompt communication of any obstacles you encounter and don't hesitate to request support when necessary. Uphold the company's values and principles in your actions, as doing so will further demonstrate your dedication and determination.\n<br>\n<b><br>Adaptability and Resilience\n</b><br>In today's fast-paced work environment, it's essential to be able to adapt and bounce back from challenges. Embrace change with optimism, and view obstacles as opportunities for personal and professional growth. Instead of letting hurdles hold you back, treat them as chances to develop and progress in your career. Adopt a mindset that is open to diverse perspectives and new experiences. Doing so will better equip you to navigate the shifting demands of your job, leading to a more resilient and thriving career.\n<br>\n<b><br>Prioritize Self-Care\n</b><br>As you move into your new role, it's crucial to prioritize your well-being. Creating a healthy work-life balance is key for your long-term success and happiness. Make sure to establish clear boundaries between your professional and personal life, and carve out time for activities that recharge and inspire you outside of work. Taking care of your physical, mental, and emotional health is vital to staying motivated, productive, and able to flourish in your career.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1831x1221.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center item features-without-image\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n        <p class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n          2010\n        </p>\n        <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n          <b>Professional photography career launch</b>\n        </h5>\n        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>Reflect on Your Achievements\n</b><br>Throughout your journey, take time to reflect on your achievements and progress. Recognize the growth you have experienced and the contributions you have made to your team and organization. Celebrating small victories and acknowledging your efforts will boost your confidence and motivation. This reflective practice not only reinforces your accomplishments but also provides insight into areas where you can continue to improve and excel.\n<br>\n<br><b>Develop a Strategic Plan\n</b><br>Create a strategic plan for your personal and professional development. Set short-term and long-term goals for your career and outline the steps needed to achieve them. This plan will provide you with a clear direction and help you stay focused on your objectives. Regularly review and adjust your planReflect on Your Achievements\n<br>\n<br>Throughout your journey, take time to reflect on your achievements and progress. Recognize the growth you have experienced and the contributions you have made to your team and organization. Celebrating small victories and acknowledging your efforts will boost your confidence and motivation. This reflective practice not only reinforces your accomplishments but also provides insight into areas where you can continue to improve and excel. as needed to ensure that you are on track and making progress toward your goals.\n<br>\n<br><b>Seek Mentorship and Networking Opportunities\n</b><br>Remember to seek out mentors within your organization or industry. A mentor can offer treasured guidance, support, and insights primarily based totally on their experience. Additionally, take advantage of networking opportunities to expand your professional connections and gain exposure to different perspectives and opportunities. Building a strong network can open doors to new career possibilities and enhance your professional growth.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}} item-wrapper \">\n        <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-5\">\n          <img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1831x1216.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\">\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
