          "_name": "news03",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"news03\" group=\"News\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n    <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Event Name\" name=\"showTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n      <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n        <b>Upcoming events</b>\n      </h3>\n      <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n      </h5>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row justify-content-center \">\n      <div class=\" col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n        <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 mb-5\">\n          <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <b>Golden Hour Mastery</b>\n            </h5>\n            <h6 class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              May 17-18, 2025\n            </h6>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>Maintain a Positive Attitude\n</b><br>\n<br>Finally, maintaining a positive attitude is essential for navigating the challenges of a new job. Approach each day with enthusiasm and a willingness to tackle new tasks and responsibilities. A positive mindset will help you overcome obstacles, build strong relationships, and contribute to a collaborative and supportive work environment.\n<br>When starting a new job, you are embarking on a journey filled with opportunities for growth, discovery, and achievement. To succeed and thrive in your new role, it's important to embrace a learning mindset, build meaningful relationships, seek clarity and feedback, demonstrate initiative and accountability, adapt to change, prioritize self-care, and commit to continuous learning.\n<br>Keep in mind that every challenge presents an opportunity for progress, and every accomplishment reflects your dedication and perseverance. With determination and a positive attitude, you have the potential to make a significant impact and excel in your career.\n<br>\n<br>Other Article: <a href=\"page22.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">Work Life Balance in the Workplace</a></p>\n            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n              <a class=\"btn btn-white\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                Learn more</a>\n            </div>\n\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        \n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v6yXh4b9bI",
          "_anchor": "news03-4i",
