          "_name": "news07",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"news07\" group=\"News\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Event Name\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Date\" name=\"showSubtitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Images\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#edefeb\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"col-12 mb-5 content-head\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                <b><br></b><br><b>Navigating the Global Job Market: A Guide for Job Seekers in South Africa</b></h3>\n            <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit.\n            </h5>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center \">\n            <div class=\" col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 active\">\n                    <div class=\"item-wrapper card-wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"card text-content\">\n                            <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                <b>Golden Hour Mastery</b>\n                            </h5>\n                            <h6 class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                May 17-18, 2025\n                            </h6>\n                            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>The job market is evolving rapidly, and it’s an exciting time to be looking for opportunities! Today, your next employer could be located in vibrant cities like New York, London, Berlin, or Dubai. The great news is that you can build a global career right from South Africa. All you need is a good Wi-Fi connection, the right skills, and some thoughtful planning.\n<br>\n<br>This friendly guide aims to help you discover incredible international opportunities, position yourself for roles around the world, and start earning in foreign currencies all without leaving your home. Let’s embark on this journey together!</b></p>\n                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                <a class=\"btn btn-white\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                    Learn more</a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper d-flex justify-content-center\">\n                            <img mbr-if=\"showImage\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1920x1275.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"1\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                    <div class=\"item-wrapper card-wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"card text-content\">\n                            <h5 class=\"mbr-card-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\">\n                                <b>Golden Hour Mastery</b>\n                            </h5>\n                            <h6 class=\"mbr-card-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-card-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n                                May 17-18, 2025\n                            </h6>\n                            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><b>🌐 Why Consider Global Jobs?\n</b><br>\n<br>Whether you're unemployed, underpaid, or simply ready for a change, looking beyond local borders can open life-changing doors.\n<br>Here’s why going global makes sense:\n<br>Higher Earning Potential: You could earn in stronger currencies like USD, EUR, or GBP.\n<br>Remote Work Freedom: Work from your bedroom, a café, or even while traveling.\n<br>Discover more\n<br>JobFinds\n<br>\n<br>Skill Growth: International exposure fast-tracks your personal and professional development.<br>\n<br>Career Options: There are more remote jobs in tech, digital marketing, virtual assistance, customer support, and more.\n<br>📊 The Top Global Skills in Demand (That South Africans Can Learn)\n<br>\n<br>You don’t need to be a coding genius or have 5 degrees to get hired internationally. Here are some of the most in-demand, accessible skills that can land you a remote job:\n<br>\n<br>💻<b> Tech Skills\n</b><br>*Web development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)\n<br>*Data analysis (Excel, SQL, Power BI)\n<br>*UI/UX design (Figma, Adobe XD)\n<br>*QA testing\n<br>\n<br>📣 <b>Marketing &amp; Content\n</b><br>*Copywriting\n<br>*SEO and blog writing\n<br>*Social media management\n<br>*Email marketing and funnels\n<br>\n<br>🤝 <b>Customer Support\n</b><br>*Virtual assistant work\n<br>*Customer service (via chat or email)\n<br>*Call center support (remote voice/chat)\n<br>\n<br>📈 <b>Business Admin &amp; Finance\n</b><br>*Bookkeeping\n<br>*Data entry\n<br>*CRM management\n<br>*Executive assistance\n<br>\n<br>🔍 <b>Where to Find Global Jobs (Legit Sites That Hire South Africans)\n</b><br>\n<b><br>I understand how challenging it can feel to find the right job, and you don’t have to rely on luck. What truly matters is knowing where to search. Here are some supportive platforms that genuinely hire South Africans every day, helping to make your job search a little easier:\n<br></b><br>1. Upwork - Freelance gigs: www.upwork.com\n<br>2. Fiverr - Freelance pack: www.fiverr.com\n<br>3. Remote OK - Full-time remote jobs:remoteok.com\n<br>4. We Work Remotely - Remote jobs: weworkremotely.com\n<br>5. Deel - Global payroll for remote workers: deel.com<br>6.Turing - Developer-focused global jobs - turing.com\n<br>7. LinkedIn - Filter by \"remote\" &amp; \"worldwide\": linkedin.com/jobs\n<br>\n<br>📝 <b>How to Make a Global-Ready CV (That Gets Noticed)\n</b><br>Most global employers receive hundreds of applications, so your CV must stand out and match international standards.\n<br>\n<br>✅ <b>CV Tips for Global Success:\n</b><br>Use a clean layout: Avoid tables and graphics. Stick to a professional format, such as a Word document or PDF.\n<br>Please adjust your summary to reflect your comfort with remote work and your ability to collaborate effectively with global teams.\n<br><br>Highlight remote tools: Include your experience with tools such as Zoom, Slack, Trello, and Google Workspace.\n<br>Include skills upfront: Present hard and soft skills in keyword-rich bullet points for easy reading.\n<br>\n<br>Write in UK or US English: Use the appropriate language based on the company’s location.\n<br>Add your time zone and availability: For example, “Based in Johannesburg (GMT+2), available from 8 am to 5 pm GMT.”<br>\n<br>🗣️ <b>Communication &amp; Interview Tips\n</b><br>International employers seek individuals with strong communication skills, particularly in both written and spoken English.\n<br>How to Prepare:\n<br>Use Grammarly: Polish your emails and cover letters for free.\n<br>Practice interview answers: Record yourself answering questions or use ChatGPT to rehearse.<br>\n<br><b>Be proactive: Ask questions in interviews, show initiative, and follow up.\n</b><br>🧠 Pro tip: Many remote interviews are done on Zoom—so make sure your background, lighting, and microphone are professional.\n<br>\n<br>💵 <b>How to Get Paid From Abroad\n</b><br>So how will you actually receive your international salary?\n<br>Here are popular platforms that work in South Africa:\n<br>\n<br>💳 <b>Payment Platforms\n</b><br>PlatformNotes\n<br>Payoneer Great for freelance payments, often used with Upwork\n<br>Wise (formerly TransferWise) Low fees, converts foreign currency into ZAR\n<br>PayPal Widely accepted but higher fees; not ideal for large salaries<br>Deel Often used by remote-first companies to pay employees legally<br>\n<br>💡<b> Tip: Always keep proof of payments and track invoices—especially for freelance gigs.\n<br></b><br>🧭<b> Your First Steps to Going Global\n</b><br>• Ready to start your global journey? Here's a step-by-step plan to follow:\n<br>• Pick one in-demand skill and commit to mastering it within 30–60 days.\n<br>• Build a simple portfolio (e.g., website, PDF, or LinkedIn showcase).\n<br>• Sign up to 2–3 global job platforms.\n<br>• Create a global-ready CV using our template.\n<br>• Apply daily, even if you get rejections.\n<br>• Practice interviews and improve English fluency.\n<br>• Set up Payoneer/Wise account early for payment readiness.\n<br>• Track your progress every week using a job tracker.\n<br>\n<br>💬<b> Real Talk: What to Expect\n</b><br>It takes effort. You may send 20–30 applications before getting your first call.\n<br>Rejection is normal. Don’t take it personally—keep learning and improving.\n<br>Confidence is key. You’re just as talented as anyone from the US or UK own it.\n<br>\n<br>🚀 <b>Final Thoughts: You Can Do This\n</b><br>South Africans are flourishing as remote designers, writers, marketers, tech experts, and virtual assistants—all while nestled in their vibrant homes in Soweto, the picturesque landscapes of Cape Town, the bustling energy of Durban, or the lively streets of Polokwane. You don’t need to embark on a journey overseas to tap into the vast potential of a global income; the international marketplace is already within your reach. All you need is the boldness to knock on that door and the relentless spirit to keep showing up, creating opportunities from the comfort of your own home.\n<br>\n<br>Other Article: <a href=\"page27.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>What to Do When Job Seekers Can't Find Employment</b></a></p>\n                            <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                                <a class=\"btn btn-white\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                    Learn more</a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"image-wrapper d-flex justify-content-center\">\n                            <img mbr-if=\"showImage\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-5-1920x1280.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\" data-slide-to=\"1\" data-bs-slide-to=\"2\">\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v6zd7YD7o0",
