          "_name": "content14",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" group=\"Content\" class=\"content14\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n    \n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>More Articles</b></h2>\n                <ul class=\"list mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".list\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                    <li><a href=\"page28.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>CV / Resume Writing Tips</b></a><br>Learn how to create a CV that grabs attention and gets shortlisted fast.</li><li><a href=\"page18.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Job-Hunting Success Kit</b></a><br>Everything you need to stay organized, confident, and competitive in your job search.</li><li><a href=\"page27.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>What to Do When You Can’t Find a Job</b></a><br>Realistic steps to reset your strategy and keep moving forward when nothing is working.</li><li><a href=\"page19.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>A Guide for New Employees in the Workplace</b></a><br>How to navigate your first 90 days and make a strong impression at your new job.</li><li><a href=\"page5.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>How to Land a Job in South Africa in 30 Days or Less</b></a><br>A practical, step-by-step plan to help you move from job searching to job secured—without wasting time.</li>\n                    <li><a href=\"page6.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>The Best Companies to Work for in South Africa in 2026</b></a><br>Explore top employers offering growth, stability, and competitive benefits across different industries.</li>\n                    <li><a href=\"page14.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Why Remote Work Matters for South Africans</b></a><br>How remote jobs are opening global opportunities and increasing earning potential locally.</li>\n                    <li><a href=\"page15.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>How to Use LinkedIn to Land Your Next Job</b></a><br>Simple strategies to turn your LinkedIn profile into a powerful job-attracting tool.</li>\n                    <li><b><a href=\"page16.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>High-Paying Jobs That Don’t Need a Degree</b></a><br></b>Discover in-demand careers where skills matter more than formal qualifications.</li><li><a href=\"page25.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Mastering Your Interview</b></a><br>How to prepare, answer confidently, and stand out in any interview setting.</li><li><a href=\"page17.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>How to Get a Job With No Experience</b></a><br>Proven ways to position yourself as a strong candidate—even without work history.</li><li><a href=\"page24.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Booming Industries in South Africa</b></a><br>Where the jobs are growing and how you can position yourself to benefit.</li><li><a href=\"page30.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Relocating to South Africa: Work &amp; Living Guide</b></a><br>A complete guide for foreigners looking to live, work, and settle in South Africa.</li><li><a href=\"page23.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>The Future of Jobs Report 2025 (Simplified)</b></a><br>What the latest trends mean for your career and how to stay ahead.</li><li><a href=\"page20.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Job Scam Red Flags in South Africa</b></a><br>How to identify fake job offers and protect yourself from losing money.</li><li><a href=\"page29.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Courses to Boost Your Skill Set</b></a><br>Short courses that can quickly improve your employability and income potential.</li><li><a href=\"page13.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Signing Employment Contracts During Mercury Retrograde</b></a><br>What to watch out for and how to protect yourself when signing job offers.</li><li><a href=\"page26.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Navigating the Global Job Market (SA Job Seekers)</b></a><br>How to position yourself for international opportunities while based in South Africa.</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
