          "_name": "features10",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features10\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <!---->\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Cards</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitleCard\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background\" name=\"cardsBg\" value=\"#fafafa\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/gallery05-1200x1200.jpg\" selected>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" checked condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#bed3f9\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"mbr-section-head\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n            <h3 mbr-if=\"showTitle\" class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><b style=\"font-size: 5rem;\">Current Jobs in South Africa</b></div></h3>\n            <h4 mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-0 mt-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\"><b>Industries - HR/ Admin, Information Technology/ Tech, Finance/ Fintech Retail &amp; Customer Service, Remote Jobs.</b></h4>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row mt-4\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 active\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://careers.discovery.co.za/job/Sandton-1-Discovery-Place-Learnership-Long-Term-Insurance-PWD-Gaut/1373961133/\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Learnership: Long Term Insurance | Discovery</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                                Johannesburg, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">The Long Term Insurance Learnership (PWD) is a great entry-level opportunity for young individuals looking to build a career in financial services while gaining a recognised qualification. This programme combines classroom learning with real workplace experience, where you’ll support client services, assist with medical aid queries, claims, and basic administration in a call centre environment. It’s ideal for candidates with Matric who are eager to learn, develop professional skills, and gain hands-on experience while working towards an NQF Level 4 qualification in long-term insurance.</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://iagjme.fa.ocs.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/CX_1005/job/1542/?utm_medium=jobshare&utm_source=External+Job+Share\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Housekeeping | Hollywoodbets</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">\n                                Cape Town, Western Cape, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            The Housekeeper role offers a great opportunity for someone who takes pride in maintaining a clean, organised, and welcoming environment. The position involves ensuring the branch remains neat and hygienic at all times, including cleaning floors, work areas, furniture, restrooms, and surrounding areas while properly managing waste and cleaning supplies. This role is ideal for someone with housekeeping experience who is reliable, detail-oriented, and comfortable working in a fast-paced environment where cleanliness and presentation are important.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://job-boards.greenhouse.io/takealotcom/jobs/7672061\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Finance Analyst | takealot group</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">Cape Town, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Takealot, South Africa’s leading online retailer, is hiring a talented professional to join its fast-growing team. This role offers the chance to work in a dynamic e-commerce environment where innovation, collaboration, and performance are key. The successful candidate will contribute to improving operations, supporting business goals, and delivering exceptional experiences to customers across the country. If you’re passionate about technology, problem-solving, and growth, this is an exciting opportunity to build your career with one of the most recognised digital brands in South Africa.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://fa-etyi-saasfaprod1.fa.ocs.oraclecloud.com/hcmUI/CandidateExperience/en/sites/MrPriceGroupCareers/job/4238/?utm_medium=jobshare&utm_source=External+Job+Share\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>L&amp;D Programme Coordinator | Mr Price Group</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">Durban, KwaZulu-Natal, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Mr Price Group is offering an exciting opportunity for someone ready to grow their career in a fast-moving retail business known for energy, innovation, and strong South African brands. This role is perfect for a driven candidate who enjoys working in a dynamic environment, contributing to day-to-day operations, supporting business goals, and being part of a team that keeps one of the country’s leading retail groups moving forward. If you’re looking for a chance to gain solid experience, build your skills, and join a company with real growth potential, this is definitely one to watch.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://oldmutual.wd3.myworkdayjobs.com/en-US/Old_Mutual_Careers/job/MFC-Sales-Agent--Tembisa-_JR-73917?locationCountry=4db3c26940b944919b83612cc1193eed\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Sales Agent | Old Mutual&nbsp;</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">Thembisa, Midrand,&nbsp; Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            Old Mutual is hiring a Sales Agent in Tembisa, offering a great entry-level opportunity for individuals who want to start or grow a career in the financial services industry. The role focuses on building and maintaining a client base, marketing and selling Old Mutual’s financial products, and helping customers improve their financial wellbeing while meeting sales targets. This position is ideal for motivated and goal-driven candidates with strong communication skills, a Matric certificate, and an interest in sales, with training and development support provided to help you grow your career.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://careers.anewhotels.com/jobs/7260993-receptionist-kwazulu-natal-hluhluwe\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Receptionist | ANEW Hotels and Resorts</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">Hluhluwe,&nbsp;KwaZulu-Natal, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            The Receptionist role offers a great opportunity for someone who enjoys working with people and creating a welcoming environment in the hospitality industry. The position involves assisting guests with check-ins and check-outs, managing reservations, answering calls, and ensuring visitors receive excellent service throughout their stay. It’s ideal for someone who is organised, friendly, and comfortable working in a fast-paced hotel environment while building valuable customer service experience.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://job-boards.greenhouse.io/jumo/jobs/7578615\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Analytics Engineer| JUMO</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">South Africa, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            The Analytics Engineer role offers an exciting opportunity for someone passionate about data and problem-solving in a fast-growing fintech environment. The position involves working with stakeholders and data teams to analyse data, investigate business problems, perform quality checks on datasets, and build reports or dashboards that support decision-making. This role is ideal for candidates with strong analytical skills, experience with databases and data queries, and an interest in transforming complex data into meaningful insights that drive business performance.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://firstrand.wd3.myworkdayjobs.com/en-US/FRB/job/Sales-Coordinator-2_R47645?utm_source=chatgpt.com&locationCountry=4db3c26940b944919b83612cc1193eed\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Sales Coordinator-2 | FNB</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">Johannesburg, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            The Sales Coordinator 2 role is a strong opportunity for someone who enjoys keeping things organised behind the scenes while supporting a busy sales team. The position focuses on handling administrative tasks, coordinating sales-related activities, and helping ensure smooth day-to-day operations so the team can perform effectively. It’s well suited to someone who is detail-oriented, proactive, and comfortable working in a fast-paced environment where strong communication and coordination skills really matter. The FirstRand careers site describes the role as supporting the sales team through administrative work and smooth sales operations.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://jobs.concentrix.com/job/?id=R1658753\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Customer Service Associate | Concentix</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">Durban, Full time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            The Customer Service Associate role is a solid opportunity for someone with call centre experience who enjoys helping people and solving problems in a fast-paced environment. Based in Durban, this position involves handling customer queries as the first point of contact, resolving issues efficiently, updating records, and promoting products and services while delivering strong customer support. It’s a great fit for someone with at least 6 months of customer service experience, good communication skills, computer literacy, and the ability to work shifts in a 24/7 environment.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"top-line row\" mbr-if=\"showTitleCard\">\n                        <div class=\"col\">\n                            <h4 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".card-title\"><a href=\"https://absa.wd3.myworkdayjobs.com/en-US/ABSAcareersite/job/Executive-Assistant_R-15984918\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\"><b>Executive Assistant | ABSA</b></a></h4>\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"col-auto\">\n                            <p class=\"price mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".price\">Johannesburg, Full-time</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"bottom-line\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style \" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\">\n                            The Executive Assistant role is a strong opportunity for someone who thrives on keeping senior leadership organised, focused, and supported in a fast-paced corporate environment. This hybrid Johannesburg-based position involves managing schedules, coordinating meetings, handling important communication, preparing documents, and helping ensure daily operations run smoothly at executive level. It’s a great fit for someone who is polished, highly organised, discreet, and confident working with multiple priorities while adding real value behind the scenes. The role is listed as hybrid and based in Johannesburg.\n                        </p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
