        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            "& when (@reverseContent)": {
              ".row": {
                "flex-direction": "row-reverse"
              }
            },
            "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
              ".image-wrapper": {
                "margin-bottom": "1rem"
              }
            },
            ".row": {
              "align-items": "center"
            },
            ".image-wrapper": {
              "@media (max-width: 991px)": {
                "padding": "1rem"
              }
            },
            ".text-wrapper": {
              "@media (min-width: 992px)": {
                "padding": "0 2rem"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#000000"
            }
          },
          "_name": "article02",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"start article2\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"8\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n\t\t</fieldset>\n\t\t<header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n\t<div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}} image-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/mbr-1357x905.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-12 col-md-12 col-lg\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"text-wrapper align-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Meet the Heart\n</b><div><b>Behind JobFinds</b></div></h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text align-left mbr-fonts-style mb-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Hi, I’m <b>Pride</b>, founder of <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">JobFinds</a>, and a <b>Senior IT Recruiter </b>and<b> HR Consultant</b> with over 10 years of experience in the South African job market.<br><br>Over the years, I have worked with both job seekers and employers across industries including banking, healthcare, IT, finance, and business consulting. I have screened thousands of CVs, supported hiring processes at different levels, and gained firsthand insight into what employers look for when selecting candidates.<br><br>I created <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">JobFinds</a> to help people access real opportunities, practical career guidance, and support that can make the job-search process feel clearer and more manageable. Having also experienced unemployment myself, I understand how discouraging and overwhelming the job market can feel.<br><br>What I have seen time and time again is that many people miss out on opportunities not because they lack potential, but because they do not always have the right guidance, tools, or visibility.<br><br>That is why <a href=\"index.html\" class=\"text-primary\" target=\"_blank\">JobFinds</a> exists.<br><br>My goal is to make job searching more accessible, more empowering, and more effective by sharing direct vacancies, useful resources, and career advice that genuinely helps people move forward with confidence.<br><br>Let’s find your next opportunity.<br>\n<br><b>With love, purpose and Jobs</b><br><b>\n</b><br><b>Pride N.</b><br><b>JobFinds - Founder</b></p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"mailto:jobfinds4u@gmail.com?subject=JobFinds%20Email\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Contact Me</a></div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v5nf2AhMAN",
          "_anchor": "article02-2l",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
            "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)",
            "background-color": "@bgColor",
            "& when (@reverseContent)": {
              ".row": {
                "flex-direction": "row-reverse"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "color": "#000000"
            }
          },
          "_name": "article15",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article15\" group=\"Article\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"reverseContent\" title=\"Reverse\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"0\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" value=\"7\" step=\"1\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" name=\"bgColor\" value=\"#ffffff\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-md\">\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\">\n                <b>Photography as Narrative</b>\n                </h5>\n                <h6 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-4\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\"><b>JobFinds exists to empower you with the tools, knowledge, and confidence to take control of your job search—step by step.</b></h6>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n              <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style mt-0 mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\"><br>💡 Why JobFinds Exists? Job hunting can be stressful, frustrating, and discouraging, especially when you are sending out applications and hearing nothing back. I understand how difficult that experience can be. Through years of working in recruitment and HR, I have seen how often talented people miss out on opportunities because they do not always have access to the right guidance, tools, or support<br> \n<br>🚀 Offerings At JobFinds, we believe that everyone deserves access to practical job-hunting help—without paying thousands in consultant fees. We provide: 🎯 Job-search guides tailored to the South African market📝 CV and interview resources designed to help job seekers present themselves more confidently 📦 Digital toolkits for both job seekers and small business recruiters 💡 Career tips, opportunities, and motivation shared through our digital platforms<br>\n<br>📍 Who We Serve? Graduates starting out, Parents returning to work, Professionals ready for change, Ambitious job seekers who want to grow, Small businesses looking for straightforward hiring support</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "v5nflI0cvG",
          "_anchor": "article15-2m",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
